[[File:Athletes.jpg|right|150px|Athlete's foot]] ;Athlete's Foot Athlete's foot (also called ringworm of the foot and tinea pedis) is a fungal infection of the foot, especially between the toes. Essential oils that are partucularly helpful in treating athlete's foot include [[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Tagetes|tagetes]], [[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Lavender|lavender]], [[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Geranium|geranium]] and [[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Tea Tree|tea tree]], for their anti-fungal properties. ==Treatment== Essential oils can be applied to the feet in the bath, soaking in a foot bath or as a warm compress. They can also be applied using a carrier oil‚Äîcalendula oil is a good one to use. The feet should be treated every morning and evening. It's also important to make sure that feet are dried thoroughly after washing, to avoid letting them stay moist, and that socks are changed frequently. Allowing the feet to be open to the air helps, although it's also important to avoid infecting other people, so don't walk barefoot in public places.
==Effective oils== *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Benzoin|Benzoin]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Clove|Clove]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Eucalyptus|Eucalyptus]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Geranium|Geranium]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Lavender|Lavender]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Lemon|Lemon]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Lemon Eucalyptus|Lemon Eucalyptus]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Lemongrass|Lemongrass]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Myrrh|Myrrh]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Palmarosa|Palmarosa]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Tagetes|Tagetes]] *[[Complete Guide to Essential Oils/A to Z of essential oils/Tea Tree|Tea Tree]] {{Wikipedia|Athlete's foot}}
