== Other forms == The various tenses of the verb av√© can be combined with other verbs' participles to create many different verbal times:
*'''Hi magnate'''. (You '''have eaten''') *'''Hive magnate'''. (You '''had eaten''') *'''Avisse magnate''' nzi mm√≥. (You '''would have eaten''' by now.) *'''Arr√¨ magnate''' ggia. (You '''might have eaten''' by now.)*rarely used, often replaced by conditional.

