<big>'''Rectal Cancer Review'''</big>
*Surgical margin **R0 typically defined as >1 mm **Prognostic impact on LR and OS *Neoadjuvant chemo-RT **Superior over adjuvant chemo-RT: German Rectal Trial **Superior over neoadjuvant RT alone: EORTC 22921 and FFCD 9203 ***No difference in OS, 5-year ~65% ***Significant benefit for LR 16-17% -> 8-9% ***R0 ~90%; ypCR 15-20%

